name: Ahana's Genesis
description: Octomint is so excited to be able to mint Ahana’s Genesis Octo for her! Ahana is a four-year old artist from Hyderabad. She loves to draw all kinds of creatures. This is an original drawing of an octopus made entirely from her imagination!! Proceeds will be sent to Ahana's mommy, who will keep them for her until she grows up.
